# Copilot token used as the Hindsight server's LLM API key. Hindsight calls the
# GitHub Copilot enterprise endpoint as an OpenAI-compatible provider; embeddings
# and reranking run locally inside the container, so only the chat LLM key here.
#
# Source: your omp Copilot login — the `github-copilot` oauth credential's
# `access` token in ~/.omp/agent/agent.db. Stable until that token expires.
#
# Copy to .env.hindsight (gitignored) and fill in the value.
HINDSIGHT_API_LLM_API_KEY=
